name: MAGGUS MASKARI II
description:
Who is behind all this masks?  Maggus Maskari could be anyone, learning to control the 5D version of the self. Smooth dancing  900 x 648px animated GIF, 64 colors, clean. 

Temple of Masks is a collaborative project created for Virtual Burning Man 2021. Part of a series of videoart and animated NFT´s by Cryptofangs.

Credits:
Video and Postproduction - Cryptofangs
Artistic Direction - Cryptofangs / Jason Gronlund
Mask Maker and Sculptor - Jason Gronlund
Starring - Hanna-Katarina / Guyphytsy Aldalai
Original Music - Inverted Forest / Mikey Brezinski
Special Thanks - Burning Man Arts
